=====================
== Cache-Directory ==
=====================

This directory holds all file data that is created or changed during the game.
It must be writable by the wbeserver user.
Execute the following command:

	chmod 777 -R cache

to allow the webserver to write to the cache directory.

The cache directory holds the following subdirectories:

- admin: admin file base
- allianceprofiles: Images for the alliance page
- avatars: Avatar images for the alliance forum
- imagepacks: generated downloadable imagepacks
- out: some generated graphics
- rss: rss feeds
- user_xml: xml files of deleted users
- userprofiles: Images of users
- xml: other xml stuff

